'''Coal''' is the highest paying cargo at the start of the game and is delivered straight from [[en/Manual/Base Set/Industries/Coal Mine]] to [[en/Manual/Base Set/Industries/Power Station]] without the need for any intermediate processing, enabling very simple connecting routes.

==Estrategias==
Coal is often used as a money maker at the start of games, especially in ''#openttdcoop'' games that use it exclusively until they begin building the actual network.

